  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<ul>
<li>Sleeps 3-6, in three Continental twin bedrooms (on one floor).</li>
<li><strong>Middle Floor:</strong> Entrance to apartment, open-plan living/dining area with TV, DVD player, fully-equipped kitchen, south-facing balcony and large terrace with covered seating area and wonderful views of the Matterhorn and Zermatt village.</li>
<li><strong>Bedrooms:</strong> Bedroom 1 has private adjacent bath/wc. Bedrooms 2 and 3 each have terrace access, and share one adjacent bath/wc.</li>
</ul>]]></roomsDescription>
